messages.messageBody:
I remember someone's daughter looking for a Barbie skateboard (Ren?) but
thought maybe other girls might like one too. So, I just received the
Fisher-Price Xmas catalog and it's in there. You can order online at
Fisher-price.com or 800-747-8697
It's F7-P77559...$22. and of course they even have pink and purple
protective gear if she wants to go all out!

Just thought this might save someone from hunting it down in December.
And no I don't make commision off of it! <g>

Sharon
